🛣️ Highway Guard: AI-Powered Accident Response System
"Saving Lives in the Golden Hour"
📌 Project Overview
Highway Guard ek advanced mobile-based safety solution hai jo specifically High-Speed Highways par hone wale accidents ko detect aur report karne ke liye banaya gaya hai. Yeh app phone ke sensors aur satellite connectivity (Starlink) ka use karke instant emergency alerts bhejta hai, un jagaho par bhi jahan mobile network nahi hota.
🚀 Key Features
 * Intelligent Highway Sensing: App sirf tab active hoti hai jab GPS detect karta hai ki user Highway par hai aur speed 60 km/h se zyada hai (Battery bachane ke liye).
 * High-Frequency Monitoring (100Hz): Impact detect karne ke liye Accelerometer aur Gyroscope ka high-speed data use hota hai.
 * Dual-Verification Logic: Accident confirm karne ke liye hum teen cheezein match karte hain:
   * G-Force Spike: Sudden impact detection.
   * GPS Speed Drop: Speed ka turant 100 se 0 hona.
   * Acoustic Signature: Crash ki awaaz ka analysis (Optional).
 * The 10-Second Fail-Safe: Accident ke baad 10-second ka timer chalta hai. Agar user "Cancel" nahi karta, toh alert automatic chala jata hai.
 * No-Signal Starlink Integration: Agar cellular network (4G/5G) fail ho jaye, toh app Starlink Direct-to-Cell technology use karke emergency SMS/Data packet bhejti hai.
 * Priority Dispatch: Sabse pehle local Highway Patrol/NHAI Number ko alert jata hai, uske baad Ambulance aur Police ko.
🛠️ Technical Stack
| Component | Technology |
|---|---|
| Mobile App | Flutter / React Native |
| Sensors | Accelerometer, Gyroscope, GPS (High-Frequency Sampling) |
| Backend | Node.js / Firebase (for real-time data sync) |
| Satellite Connectivity | Starlink Direct-to-Cell API (2026 Standard) |
| Emergency Protocols | RapidSOS / Twilio API for Automated Calls |
🛰️ How It Works (The Workflow)
 * Background Activity: App low-power mode mein movement detect karti hai.
 * Detection: Jab sudden impact hota hai, app background se High-Frequency Mode mein switch ho kar data analyze karti hai.
 * User Interface: Screen par ek emergency dashboard pop-up hota hai with a 10-second countdown.
 * Data Transmission: * Signal Available: Server ko full data packet (GPS, Speed, Medical ID) bhejta hai.
   * No Signal: Starlink ke zariye ek 50-character "Emergency Code" bhejta hai.
 * Rescue: Highway authorities ko exact location milti hai, jisse response time 50% kam ho jata hai.
🛡️ Edge Cases Handled
 * Phone Broken in Crash: Server "Last-Gasp" packet monitor karta hai. Agar impact ke baad signal gayab ho jaye, toh ise "Confirmed Crash" maana jata hai.
 * False Positives: Phone girne ya sudden brake lagane par alert trigger nahi hoga kyunki GPS speed match nahi karegi.
 * Privacy: Data encryption ke saath sirf emergency ke waqt hi location share hoti hai.
👨‍💻 Installation & Setup
 * Clone the repository: git clone https://github.com/your-link/highway-guard
 * Install dependencies: npm install
 * Add API Keys for Google Maps and Starlink.
 * Run on Device: flutter run (High-frequency sensors virtual emulator par kaam nahi karte, physical device zaroori hai).
🏆 Vision
Hamara goal hai ki har saal highway par hone wali 1.5 lakh+ deaths ko technology ke zariye kam kiya jaye.
